#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
monet-locker — Experimental art-first lock screen for XFCE/X11.

Flow:
  INITIAL   Painting-of-day + quote shown across 3 monitors (via curator.py).
            Museum-style layout; no effects, no chrome.
  UNLOCK    On first input event, a subtle "Wake up, Neo..." typewriter
            appears top-left of the main monitor. Login card fades in at
            center-bottom with WhiteSur-Dark aesthetic. ~2.5s total.
  AUTH      PAM auth via pamela. Success → destroy + exit 0. Fail → shake +
            "Incorrect password", retry.

Modes:
  --preview     Windowed (1280x720), no grab, no PAM (exit on Return/Esc).
  default       Fullscreen multi-monitor, keyboard/pointer grab, PAM auth.

Kill-switch: `touch /tmp/monet-locker-v2-killswitch` force-exits.
"""

